<BaseLayout title="Pricing — Janaushdhi" description="Janaushdhi is free. No subscriptions, no paid tiers.">
  <div class="page prose">
    <span class="pill">Pricing</span>
    <h1 style="margin-top:12px;">It's free.</h1>
    <p>Janaushdhi has no paid tiers, no subscriptions, no upgrade prompts. The whole catalogue is available without signing in.</p>
    <p>Hosting is on Cloudflare Pages free tier. If we ever introduce a sponsor block, it will be a single non-tracking link in the footer — never inline, never an ad network.</p>
    <h2>Why free?</h2>
    <p>Generic medicine price intelligence is a public good. Charging users to find affordable medication would defeat the point of the Jan Aushadhi scheme.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:32px;"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/browse/">Browse the catalogue →</a></p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
